{
  "stem": "23626.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I find a good time to tell him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That a month later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was in bed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Helen said that this was-- she was almost leaving, because they went to bed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, he came looking for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Could you imagine the fact that I wasn't there, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] because we were ordered to sleep not in the villa?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Would I have been there, I wouldn't be here telling [LAUGHS] you this story.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That moment when I came up to the room when he rung that little bell, my feet were trembling.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] All he said to me, how lucky can a stupid dog be?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You are a stupid, lucky dog.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remembered what Helen told me, jawohl, Herr [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Commandeer. ?] I saw her holding him very tight around his waist.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said to make his coffee.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember spilling the coffee because my hand were trembling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, he's going to get dressed and go up to the camp and get my sisters.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I waited a day, the next day, and the following day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he didn't go for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think that, as I said from the beginning, it was in God's hands.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no reason.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no way to explain anything about him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I only know that it was meant to be.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was fortunate to have my sisters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I paid a big price, but thank God, I have my sisters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Would I have more family?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe I could do more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I met a very-- I met a boy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His name was Adam Sztap.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I guess we were more just friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We really fell in love.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
